"12 ounces uncooked cavatappi pasta","1 1/2 tablespoons unsalted butter","2 tablespoons finely chopped shallot","2 1/2 teaspoons lemon zest","1  large garlic clove, minced","3/4 cup dry white wine","1/4 cup fresh lemon juice","1 1/2 teaspoons kosher salt","3/4 cup heavy cream","1/4 cup crème fraîche","1 teaspoon all-purpose flour","1  (16-ounce) package frozen edamame, thawed","3 ounces Romano cheese, grated (about 3/4 cup)","1 cup packed baby arugula","2 tablespoons chopped fresh tarragon","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper"